---

---

<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden pt-20">
  <!-- Background grid -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(92,124,250,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(92,124,250,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:64px_64px]"></div>

  <!-- Radial gradient -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[600px] bg-brand-600/8 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center">
    <!-- Badge -->
    <div class="fade-in inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-brand-700/30 bg-brand-950/50 px-4 py-1.5 mb-8">
      <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent-green animate-pulse"></div>
      <span class="text-xs font-medium text-brand-300">Tu asistente de cálculo para inversiones</span>
    </div>

    <!-- Headline -->
    <h1 class="fade-in text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-6">
      Las matemáticas que<br />
      <span class="text-gradient">protegen tu inversión.</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Subheadline -->
    <p class="fade-in max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg sm:text-xl text-surface-200/60 mb-10 leading-relaxed">
      Margn te dice cómo repartir tu dinero, cuándo aportar y cuánto riesgo estás asumiendo realmente.
      Tú decides. Nosotros calculamos.
    </p>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="fade-in flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-16">
      <a
        href="https://app.margn.es"
        class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-brand-600 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white hover:bg-brand-500 transition-all hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(92,124,250,0.3)]"
      >
        Empieza gratis
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        href="#como-funciona"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-surface-800 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-medium text-surface-200/80 hover:border-surface-200/30 hover:text-white transition-all"
      >
        Mira cómo funciona
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="fade-in grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white">80%</div>
        <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-surface-200/50 mt-1">Mejor rendimiento por riesgo</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-accent-green">0</div>
        <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-surface-200/50 mt-1">Liquidaciones forzadas</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white">14x</div>
        <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-surface-200/50 mt-1">Recuperación tras caídas</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white">$213K</div>
        <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-surface-200/50 mt-1">Capital extra en simulación</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="fade-in text-[10px] text-surface-200/30 mt-4">
      Resultados de simulaciones con datos históricos (2015-2020). Rendimientos pasados no garantizan resultados futuros.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Scroll indicator -->
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce">
    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-surface-200/30" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3" />
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
